ters are really interested in is Int, Mana, and resists (especially magic resist, although cold and fire are close behind).  There are at least 2 other robes in the game that have the same +Mana and magic resist stats.  The extra intelligence doesn't matter, since even if you are decked out in +Mana or resist gear, at the high end you are over the HARD cap (+255!) for Int!  Make a caster toon for yourself on this site and try it out for yourself if you don't believe me.  Flowing Thought?  If you have so much as one other Flowing Thought item, this adds nothing.  That leaves AC.<br><br>Yeah, those level 60 Wizards with Dragonbane tank Velious mobs all the time.  Not!<br><br>This is the robe that made me appreciate just how good my class's epic really is.  Maybe someday...maybe.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
