are are made to be undefeatable so that there's always some unexplored territory to keep the customer allured.  (Watch, shortly after Luclin is released, give it three months, the Sleeper and Tunare will both be defeated after a miraculous patch.  But then we'll have an undefeatable Luclin on our hands, or a grandmaster Kerran nasty.)<br><br>Meaning, all in all, this is probably the single greatest achievement a guild can aspire to in EQ right now.  The loot should be of just the slightest reflection of that.  <br><br>Congrats to the casters and clerics walking away with this incredible robe.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
